ANALYSIS
This bill requires that voters residing in all municipalities that are served by a school district
vote on the closure of schools. This bill also requires school boards to hold a public meeting for such
vote,withthesameprocedureapplyingtobothsingledistrictandcooperativeschooldistricts.
